title: Compare the performance of schools and colleges in England

heading_context: Compare the performance of schools and colleges in England
chunks.html_content:
Search for primary, secondary and special needs schools and colleges near you, and compare their performance.

You can view and download:

  • exam and test results
  • Ofsted reports
  • financial information
